name: Gundam Build Fighters-Iori Rinko
description:
Rinko Iori (イオリ・リン子)

Makoto's mother, the manager of Iori Model Shop (in essence). However, she is not familiar with plastic models, especially Gundam models, and always relies on Makoto, who is her son. Her special skill is cooking, and her specialty is stir-fried wild vegetables.

To change your costume try blocking the following words.

chanchanko, apron, sleeves, dress, shirt, from above, bent over, coat, sweater, turtleneck sweater,
